logic.schemes.task

Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.schemes.Scheme
      • logic.schemes.task.Task

  • @Entity
public class Task
extends Scheme
    A Class to manage tasks jobs and roles. Needs a name to be set when creating the object. Holds and maintains the supervisor, workers and jobs variables.
